{"id":278950,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2013/02/维权网-陈庆霞发声抗议政府的人文关怀（图/","date":"2013-02-13T02:00:56Z","modified":"2013-02-13T02:00:56Z","title":"维权网 | 陈庆霞发声抗议政府的“人文关怀”（图）","content":"<p><div dir=\"ltr\"><a rel=\"nofollow\" name='more'></a></p>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-3fGtP24nJeU/URrmNTp8wPI/AAAAAAAAdCY/fidsI8FvYTg/s1600/%E5%8C%97%E7%AA%97%E6%88%B7%E5%A4%96%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E5%99%A8.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://4.bp.blogspot.com/-3fGtP24nJeU/URrmNTp8wPI/AAAAAAAAdCY/fidsI8FvYTg/s320/%E5%8C%97%E7%AA%97%E6%88%B7%E5%A4%96%E7%9A%84%E7%9B%91%E6%8E%A7%E5%99%A8.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>陈庆霞北窗外的监控器（感谢邓志波提供的图片）</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<table align=\"center\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody>\n<tr>\n<td><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-LxgrlB29qMY/URrmWloAcXI/AAAAAAAAdCg/Fgirm2pTiQg/s1600/P1000506.JPG\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"240\" src=\"http://3.bp.blogspot.com/-LxgrlB29qMY/URrmWloAcXI/AAAAAAAAdCg/Fgirm2pTiQg/s320/P1000506.JPG\" width=\"320\" /></a></td>\n</tr>\n<tr>\n<td>陈庆霞的房间内写满“冤”字</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody>\n</table>\n<div></div>\n<div><strong><span>（维权网信息员郑毅报道）春节期间，黑龙江省伊春市</span></strong><span>带岭区</span><strong><span>上访维权人士陈庆霞在网上发布题为</span></strong><span>【<b><u>这个春节真是四面楚歌</u></b>】的</span><strong><span>帖子，强烈抗议政府的</span></strong><span>“</span><strong><span>人文关怀</span></strong><span>”</span><strong><span>。</span></strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></div>\n<div></div>\n<div><strong><span>帖子中说：</span></strong><span>“政府的人文关怀已经到了无微不至。今天中午我丈夫的哥哥宋立暖再次登门警告我：</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span><span>、不要再见网友；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span><span>、不要再和网友拍照；</span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> 3</span><span>、网友是反革命。并无奈的说怕自己受牵连。……”</span><strong><span lang=\"EN-US\"></span></strong></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><a rel=\"nofollow\" target=\"_blank\" href=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Y8Pb9mKNJhY/URrmz9GQYHI/AAAAAAAAdCo/O21k64CadBI/s1600/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\"><img border=\"0\" height=\"320\" src=\"http://1.bp.blogspot.com/-Y8Pb9mKNJhY/URrmz9GQYHI/AAAAAAAAdCo/O21k64CadBI/s320/%E6%88%AA%E5%9B%BE00.jpg\" width=\"294\" /></a></div>\n<div><span><br /></span></div>\n<div><span>陈庆霞，黑龙江省伊春市带岭区</span><strong><span>上访维权人士</span></strong><span>，因为丈夫遭到不公平待遇常年上访，被当地政府部门强行安置在一所废弃的太平间里，限制人身自由达<span lang=\"EN-US\">3</span>年之久。本网在<span lang=\"EN-US\">3 </span>年前率先披露了陈庆霞被劳教的情况，。<span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span>日 官方媒体将她的遭遇曝光后，引发了社会各界的广泛关注。<span lang=\"EN-US\">1</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">24</span>日 ，伊春市带岭区宣传部公开回应此事，称是对信访人员的“人文关怀”。但截至<span lang=\"EN-US\">2013</span>年<span lang=\"EN-US\">2</span>月<span lang=\"EN-US\">12</span>日 ，陈庆霞依然没有获得人身自由，还不断受到威胁和逼迫。</span></div>\n<div><span><span lang=\"EN-US\"> </span></span></div>\n</div>\n</p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://chinadigitaltimes.us4.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=17daa75df533f6c6ff72e51ab&#038;id=b4fd4ae247\">\n<a href=\"http://eepurl.com/mstlf\">墙外新闻实时更新 欢迎订阅数字时代</a><br />\n <br /><input type=\"email\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" id=\"mce-EMAIL_in_post\" size=\"25\" style=\"display:block;\" placeholder=\"请输入您的邮件地址\" required><br />\n\t<input type=\"submit\" value=\"点击订阅\" name=\"subscribe\" style=\"height: 20px;\" id=\"in_post_subscribe\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":997,"categories":[18270,18269,20534],"tags":[16910]}